dict.string: Mobile Device User Organizational Unit Path
Mobile Device User Is Member Of
Windows only: The type of BIOS active on the computer, legacy or UEFI.

OS X only: Whether the FileVault recovery key for this computer is stored in Absolute Manage Server. In addition to "Yes" and "No", the value can be "Yes, not verified". This indicates that a recovery key for this computer is stored on the server, but it is unknown whether this key is still valid. (For example, the user may have set a different key in the meantime.)
Use Only Absolute Manage for OS Updates
